   189	### Worked example (row 1, spectrum 0, from the actual file)
   190	```
   191	mz_chunk_start = 252.96545361882283
   192	mz_chunk_values[:6] = [None, 252.96545361882283, 0.00038742706865946275, 0.00038742825540794, ...]
