    23	- Emit the data facets in the reference **chunk layout** instead of point layout; make chunked the **new default** (`--point` restores v1 point layout). Lossless (delta-encoded m/z). Numpress (Phase 3) plugs into the `mz_numpress_linear_bytes` slot later. Chromatograms stay point layout (the reference keeps them point).
    24	- Authoritative reference is `refs/mzPeak/small.chunked.mzpeak`.
